<br>
By selling the characters, SOE would be officially recognizing that characters and gear have monetary value, and could thus be liable for compensation of their players when a player suffers a loss of xp or plat or gear due to a bug.  As it is now, characters and plat and gear have no legal value -- I don't think they want to change that...<br>
<br>
